
mujhe añdhere meñ be-shak biThā diyā hotā 
magar charāġh kī sūrat jalā diyā hotā 
na raushnī koī aatī mire ta.āqub meñ 
jo apne-āp ko maiñ ne bujhā diyā hotā 
ye dard jism ke yā-rab bahut shadīd lage 
mujhe salīb pe do pal sulā diyā hotā 
ye shukr hai ki mire paas terā ġham to rahā 
vagarna zindagī ne to rulā diyā hotā 